item.title: Lambo Drifter
item.description: Cool Racing 3D games are created according to the plot of the movie about Luke Hobbs, driving through the streets of Rio de Janeiro. Discover the rewind function and get another opportunity to get around a dangerous turn or avoid a collision. Objects on the street can collapse or explode, changing the track and putting up new obstacles.
